rows.label: qst100905_msg0006
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Frozen in ice...? F-five years?!
What do you mean, five years?!

rows.label: qst100905_msg0007
rows.name:
Then what about the enemy we
were fighting back then?

rows.label: qst100905_msg0008
rows.name:
After you were frozen, a Garlus
stormed in and was defeated.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0009
rows.name: So that's what happened...

rows.label: qst100905_msg0010
rows.name: I'm sorry for suddenly attacking you.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0011
rows.name:
I thought the battle from back
then was still going on.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0012
rows.name: Everyone, thank you.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0013
rows.name: Thanks to you, I can remember Therida!

rows.label: qst100905_msg0014
rows.name:
Therida, let's rest in the
Kingdom of Luxuria for a while.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0015
rows.name:
It's been five years, so you might
be a little confused, but...

rows.label: qst100905_msg0016
rows.name: The Kingdom of Luxuria...

rows.label: qst100905_msg0017
rows.name:
Come to think of it, I wonder
what happened to the prodigal
prince of Luxuria.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0018
rows.name:
Five years means he's 25... He
must be a fine man by now!

rows.label: qst100905_msg0019
rows.name: Therida...

rows.label: qst100905_msg0020
rows.name:
When we were attacked here, wasn't
it a dangerous job you accepted
just based on the client's face?!

rows.label: qst100905_msg0021
rows.name:
Huh? Was it? I was frozen for
five years, so I forgot...

rows.label: qst100905_msg0022
rows.name:
Everyone, thank you!
Well then, see you!

rows.label: qst100905_msg0023
rows.name:
But five years is short, isn't it? If I was
going to be frozen, I'd have liked it to be
for 500 years and woken up in the future.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0024
rows.name:
After that much time, everyone
would be handsome, and I'd be
pampered as an ancient person.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0025
rows.name:
*sigh*... I'm relieved you're thinking
like your usual self, Therida, but let's
just go back to the city for now.

rows.label: qst100905_msg0026
rows.name: You're right.
